      "lemma": "\u03b4\u03b5\u03b9\u03bd\u03cc\u03c2",
      "partOfSpeech": "adjective",
      "definition": "clever, skilled; terrible, fearsome",
      "pronunciation": { "classical": "/dei\u032f.n\u00f3s/" },
