      "pronunciation": { "classical": "/r\u030ct\u025b\u0301\u02d0.t\u0254\u02d0r/" },
      "exampleSentence": "\u03bf\u1f50 \u03b3\u03ac\u03c1 \u03b5\u1f30\u03bc\u03b9 \u1fe5\u03ae\u03c4\u03c9\u03c1.",
      "exampleTranslation": "For I am not an orator.",
      "notes": "Transliteration: rh\u0113t\u014dr. Root of English 'rhetoric'. Socrates ironically claims he lacks oratorical skill."
